  "prompt": "How do I collect movie tickets booked on BookMyShow?",
  "response": "To collect movie tickets booked on BookMyShow, you generally follow these steps:\n\n1. **Booking Tickets**:\n   - Open the BookMyShow app or visit the BookMyShow website.\n   - Log in to your account if you haven't already.\n   - Select the city, movie, and the cinema you prefer.\n   - Choose the date and showtime.\n   - Select your seats and proceed to checkout.\n\n2. **Payment**:\n   - Choose your payment method (credit/debit card, net banking, UPI, wallets, etc.).\n   - Complete the payment.\n\n3. **Confirmation**:\n   - Once your payment is processed, BookMyShow will send you a booking confirmation.\n   - You will receive an email and/or SMS containing the booking details and a QR code.\n   - You can also view and manage your booking details within the BookMyShow app under 'My ShowBookings'.\n\n4. **Collecting Physical Tickets**:\n   - Some cinemas require you to collect physical tickets.\n   - Reach the cinema box office with sufficient time before the show starts.\n   - Show your confirmation email/SMS or QR code at the box office counter or ticket kiosk to get your physical tickets.\n\n5. **Using E-Tickets**:\n   - Many cinemas accept e-tickets.\n   - You can directly show the QR code on your mobile device at the cinema entrance.\n   - The staff will scan the QR code.\n\nEnsure you read any specific instructions provided by BookMyShow or the cinema regarding ticket collection and entry policies.",
